    {
      "name": "[G1] Taproom",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>The taproom is a well-lit and airy room; it can become noisy during market days. Cold food and beer are served during the day. Guests that wish a full, hot meal are invited to return in the evenings.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
