      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>Olmael makes a decent porter and light ales in his brewhouse. He buys cider and stronger liquors from Zarel Flaeren (@UUID[JournalEntry.ovVLKx3hZhZFZq2J.JournalEntryPage.7Qz3FyveCo33TVyM]{[52] Cottar Zarel Faleren}).</p>",
