    {
      "name": "[G7] Olmel Family Quarters",
      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p>Olmael’s family lives above the side bar. His mother occupies the bed next to the door. Granny Semel came to live with her son, Olmael, after being found wandering the green in her shift. She claimed to have been looking for her geese. Friends and relatives started searching for the missing fowl but, when someone remembered that she didn’t keep geese, the search was called off and Granny sent to live with her eldest son for her own safety.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
